<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8">
	<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
	<title><%= title || "Courses" %></title>
	<style>
		.content {
			max-width: 1200px;
			margin: 40px auto 70px;
			padding: 0 18px;
		}

		.panel {
			background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
			border-radius: 18px;
			padding: 26px;
			border: 1px solid var(--line);
			box-shadow: var(--shadow);
		}

		.grid {
			display: grid;
			grid-template-columns: repeat(3, minmax(0, 1fr));
			gap: 16px;
			margin-top: 16px;
		}

		.card {
			background: #fffaf4;
			border: 1px solid var(--line);
			border-radius: 14px;
			padding: 16px;
			box-shadow: 0 10px 18px rgba(27, 20, 15, 0.08);
			display: grid;
			gap: 10px;
		}

		.card p {
			margin: 0;
			color: var(--muted);
			font-size: 14px;
		}

		.enroll-btn {
			padding: 8px 14px;
			border-radius: 999px;
			border: none;
			background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent), var(--accent-2));
			color: #ffffff;
			font-size: 13px;
			font-weight: 600;
			cursor: pointer;
			justify-self: start;
		}

		.enroll-btn:hover {
			opacity: 0.92;
		}

		@media (max-width: 980px) {
			.grid {
				grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
			}
		}

		@media (max-width: 640px) {
			.grid {
				grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			}
		}
	</style>
</head>
<body>
	<%- include("partials/navbar") %>

	<main class="content">
		<section class="panel">
			<h1>Courses</h1>
			<p>Browse the learning tracks available in the dashboard.</p>

			<div class="grid">
				<div class="card">
					<h3>Frontend Basics</h3>
					<p>HTML, CSS, and responsive design fundamentals.</p>
					<form action="/enroll" method="POST">
						<input type="hidden" name="course" value="Frontend Basics">
						<input type="hidden" name="schedule" value="Mon & Wed · 10:00 AM">
						<input type="hidden" name="live" value="Friday · 6:00 PM">
						<button class="enroll-btn" type="submit">Enroll</button>
					</form>
				</div>
				<div class="card">
					<h3>React Fundamentals</h3>
					<p>Components, hooks, and state management patterns.</p>
					<form action="/enroll" method="POST">
						<input type="hidden" name="course" value="React Fundamentals">
						<input type="hidden" name="schedule" value="Tue & Fri · 11:00 AM">
						<input type="hidden" name="live" value="Saturday · 4:00 PM">
						<button class="enroll-btn" type="submit">Enroll</button>
					</form>
				</div>
				<div class="card">
					<h3>Python for Beginners</h3>
					<p>Core syntax, loops, functions, and problem solving.</p>
					<form action="/enroll" method="POST">
						<input type="hidden" name="course" value="Python for Beginners">
						<input type="hidden" name="schedule" value="Mon & Wed · 5:00 PM">
						<input type="hidden" name="live" value="Thursday · 6:30 PM">
						<button class="enroll-btn" type="submit">Enroll</button>
					</form>
				</div>
				<div class="card">
					<h3>JavaScript Core</h3>
					<p>Variables, functions, DOM, and asynchronous flow.</p>
					<form action="/enroll" method="POST">
						<input type="hidden" name="course" value="JavaScript Core">
						<input type="hidden" name="schedule" value="Tue & Thu · 2:00 PM">
						<input type="hidden" name="live" value="Saturday · 5:00 PM">
						<button class="enroll-btn" type="submit">Enroll</button>
					</form>
				</div>
				<div class="card">
					<h3>Backend Essentials</h3>
					<p>Express, MongoDB, sessions, and authentication.</p>
					<form action="/enroll" method="POST">
						<input type="hidden" name="course" value="Backend Essentials">
						<input type="hidden" name="schedule" value="Mon & Thu · 4:00 PM">
						<input type="hidden" name="live" value="Sunday · 3:00 PM">
						<button class="enroll-btn" type="submit">Enroll</button>
					</form>
				</div>
				<div class="card">
					<h3>MongoDB Basics</h3>
					<p>Schema design, queries, and aggregation pipelines.</p>
					<form action="/enroll" method="POST">
						<input type="hidden" name="course" value="MongoDB Basics">
						<input type="hidden" name="schedule" value="Tue & Thu · 3:00 PM">
						<input type="hidden" name="live" value="Friday · 5:30 PM">
						<button class="enroll-btn" type="submit">Enroll</button>
					</form>
				</div>
				<div class="card">
					<h3>UI/UX Foundations</h3>
					<p>Research, wireframes, and interaction design basics.</p>
					<form action="/enroll" method="POST">
						<input type="hidden" name="course" value="UI/UX Foundations">
						<input type="hidden" name="schedule" value="Mon & Thu · 12:30 PM">
						<input type="hidden" name="live" value="Sunday · 2:00 PM">
						<button class="enroll-btn" type="submit">Enroll</button>
					</form>
				</div>
				<div class="card">
					<h3>Data Structures</h3>
					<p>Arrays, stacks, queues, and linked lists practice.</p>
					<form action="/enroll" method="POST">
						<input type="hidden" name="course" value="Data Structures">
						<input type="hidden" name="schedule" value="Wed & Fri · 9:00 AM">
						<input type="hidden" name="live" value="Saturday · 1:00 PM">
						<button class="enroll-btn" type="submit">Enroll</button>
					</form>
				</div>
				<div class="card">
					<h3>Git & GitHub</h3>
					<p>Version control, branching workflows, collaboration.</p>
					<form action="/enroll" method="POST">
						<input type="hidden" name="course" value="Git & GitHub">
						<input type="hidden" name="schedule" value="Tue & Thu · 6:00 PM">
						<input type="hidden" name="live" value="Sunday · 11:00 AM">
						<button class="enroll-btn" type="submit">Enroll</button>
					</form>
				</div>
			</div>
		</section>
	</main>

	<%- include("partials/footer") %>
</body>
</html>
